data.description: Fully available is this beautifully maintained and move-in-ready home located in the heart of Newburgh's West-End. This charming property offers a perfect blend of classic architecture and modern amenities, making it an ideal place to call home. This house exudes classic appeal with its well-maintained exterior, featuring a welcoming rocking chair porch. Step inside to discover an open living area filled with natural light, highlighted by gleaming hardwood floors and crown molding. The kitchen is a dream for preparing daily meals, boasting plenty of countertop area, stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient pass-through breakfast bar. The generously sized bedrooms upstairs offer comfortable living space, each with its own unique character. Two smaller bedrooms combine to make a 230 sq/ft master bedroom creating a welcoming, oversized retreat. Back down through the sliding glass doors, is both privacy and tranquility with a spacious deck, perfect for entertaining guests, enjoying your morning coffee or simply taking in the fresh air. Outside, you'll also find an exceedingly large 1-car garage for off-street parking with an incredible amount of space, as well as a loft for even more storage.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming house your new home. It offers a perfect combination of old-world charm and modern comfort in a convenient and sought-after location. Schedule a viewing today and start envisioning your life in this delightful Newburgh residence.
